# Shared infrastructure secrets consumed by podman-compose.yml.
# Copy this file to `.env` and replace every value with a strong, unique secret.
# The resulting `.env` is git-ignored and must never be committed. See SECRETS.md.

### Postgres
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=changeme-strong-db-password

### Redis
REDIS_PASSWORD=changeme-strong-redis-password

### Grafana admin (consumed by podman-compose.yml)
GRAFANA_ADMIN_USER=admin
GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD=changeme-strong-grafana-password

### AWS Secrets Manager (production, optional) — see SECRETS.md
# When set, backend/agent load secrets from this secret (a JSON object of ENV_KEY: value)
# at startup, so you don't ship real secret values in service .env files.
# AWS_SECRETS_MANAGER_SECRET_ID=notelite/prod
# AWS_REGION=us-east-1
